class_free, ldap_scherr2str - Schema definition handling routines

LIBRARY
OpenLDAP LDAP (libldap, -lldap)

SYNOPSIS
#include &amp;lt;ldap.h&amp;gt;
#include &amp;lt;ldap_schema.h&amp;gt;

