LDAP_SCHERR_NORIGHTPAREN
Missing closing parenthesis.

LDAP_SCHERR_NODIGIT
Expecting digit.

LDAP_SCHERR_BADNAME
Expecting a name.

LDAP_SCHERR_BADDESC
Bad description.

LDAP_SCHERR_BADSUP
Bad superiors.

